      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of June 11 Long Island Journal picture caption about New Hyde Park, NY, gym that caters to elderly which misidentified gym president Richard Markx (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A picture caption with the Long Island Journal column last Sunday, about a New Hyde Park gym that caters to the elderly, misidentified the man shown supervising exercise. He was Richard Markx, president of the gym, not Tom LaViano, its director.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>A picture caption with the Long Island Journal column last Sunday, about a New Hyde Park gym that caters to the elderly, misidentified the man shown supervising exercise. He was Richard Markx, president of the gym, not Tom LaViano, its director.</p>
      </block>
